Draped in garlands, Bhumika Shrestha on Monday became .css-jfmysa{display:inline;word-break:break-word;} .css-1ankfgb{cursor:pointer;display:inline;word-break:break-word;} Nepal ’s first transgender woman lawmaker, marking a proud milestone for the marginalised community in the Himalayan nation.

